<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2316941'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2316941.Orson_Scott_Card_s_InterGalactic_Medicine_Show"><img alt="Orson Scott Card&#39;s InterGalactic Medicine Show: An Anthology" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1316130004l/2316941._SX98_.jpg" />
